{"tid":184769,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"穗禾苑再創新高 高層平電梯兩房398萬連租約易手","createTime":"2017-04-03T04:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T11:25:14.000Z","uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"424b8827d0f469054a6a085b2823c807b2fcef48","tid":184769,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"樓市不斷升溫，較為低水的居屋物業獲得投資者青睞。世紀21陽光物業區域經理陳世民表示，市場新近錄得火炭穗禾苑成交，單位為E座中層12室，位處平電梯樓層，實用面積457平方呎，2房間隔，座向北面望內園景，獲投資者以398萬元連租約承接，實用面積呎價8,709元，創同類單位新高。<br />\n <br />\n陳世民透露，上址現時月租10,500元，新買家暫可享租金回報近3.2厘。原業主於2011年2月以185萬元購入物業，持貨6年至今沽售，賬面獲利213萬元離場，單位期內升值逾1.1倍。"},{"pid":"f4c361625e3d3cc35deb0492c3aaab64706c1706","tid":184769,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/184295/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/184295/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"36df73338bccb4ea0efe7a86ff3fca2908e00a9c","tid":184769,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:49:53.000Z","msg":"40年樓 殘到仆街<br />\n個大斜坡 仲要成日比維修費<br />\n返屋企行成百幾樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe851a0f212f97623a9803525947cab465a093b","tid":184769,"uid":51604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:54:28.000Z","msg":"係咪之前停車場電費分唔清嗰度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31f4b984691a53c50cd7bc43d1c4bd061768fd5","tid":184769,"uid":22247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"好撚抵，再唔買升到777萬一房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b808a0f9741c70658e7b06cc7c77dc34abd2f429","tid":184769,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"偉大領袖梁振英 帶領香港樓價節節上升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets